{"vv56:0.1":"Vimanavatthu ","vv56:0.2":"Purisavimana ","vv56:0.3":"Maharathavagga ","vv56:0.4":"6. Pathamakaraniyavimanavatthu ","vv56:1.1":"“Uccamidam manithunam vimanam, ","vv56:1.2":"Samantato dvadasa yojanani; ","vv56:1.3":"Kutagara sattasata ulara, ","vv56:1.4":"Veluriyathambha rucakatthata subha. ","vv56:2.1":"Tatthacchasi pivasi khadasi ca, ","vv56:2.2":"Dibba ca vina pavadanti vaggum; ","vv56:2.3":"Dibba rasa kamagunettha panca, ","vv56:2.4":"Nariyo ca naccanti suvannachanna. ","vv56:3.1":"Kena tetadiso vanno, ","vv56:3.2":"…pe… ","vv56:3.3":"Vanno ca te sabbadisa pabhasati”ti. ","vv56:4.1":"So devaputto attamano, ","vv56:4.2":"…pe… ","vv56:4.3":"yassa kammassidam phalam. ","vv56:5.1":"“Karaniyani punnani, ","vv56:5.2":"panditena vijanata; ","vv56:5.3":"Sammaggatesu buddhesu, ","vv56:5.4":"yattha dinnam mahapphalam. ","vv56:6.1":"Atthaya vata me buddho, ","vv56:6.2":"aranna gamamagato; ","vv56:6.3":"Tattha cittam pasadetva, ","vv56:6.4":"tavatimsupago aham. ","vv56:7.1":"Tena metadiso vanno, ","vv56:7.2":"…pe… ","vv56:7.3":"Vanno ca me sabbadisa pabhasati”ti. ","vv56:8.1":"Pathamakaraniyavimanam chattham. "}